  <brief_title>Stem Cell Transplant From Matched Unrelated or Partially Matched Related Donors</brief_title>
  <official_title>Stem Cell Transplantation From Matched Unrelated or Partially Matched Related Donors Using a Preparatory Regimen Consisting of Fractionated Total Body Irradiation (FTBI) and Cyclophosphamide (CY)</official_title>
